{"tid":2301492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個女人用求婚箍煲係咪好冇尊嚴","createTime":"2020-11-26T10:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T11:43:52.000Z","uid":256585,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45737413eb964a727fbfcb679be800ff595ba053","tid":2301492,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"直頭On9 <br />\n<br />\n慘過俾人姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/554290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F554290&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=211bc744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/554290</a><br />\n<br />\n《愛回家》謝可逸搭上貴婦　謝文欣曾求婚挽救：喊住講唔好分手<br />\n<br />\n謝文欣今日（26/11）現身電視城出席《歡樂滿東華2020》記者會。早前有指其拍拖六年圈中男友謝可逸，背她偷搭失婚貴婦CEO,更盛傳二人奉子成婚消息。文欣表示同男方最就半年前已經「被分手」，直言睇到相關報導時心情難受，「其實去到呢一刻，我都唔想再去深究，究竟個女人係唔係第三者，導致我哋分手嘅原因，就算係又點，我亦唔想再去諗。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到當時分手有否極力挽救？文欣眼紅紅表示：「當時我有喊住同佢講話唔好分手，仲提出我哋不如結婚，但佢依然覺得分開係可以令大家成長。（情傷放低未？）係需要時間，我係睇開咗嘅！（同前男友有否聯絡？）大家冇再聯絡。（大家再見亦是朋友？）將來嘅事唔諗，其實做朋友都要講緣份。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPN7xuJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPN7xuJ.png&h=75114ac9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed112678d00f486a5827cd530079fe91acd3bbd6","tid":2301492,"uid":92859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/884/521/353.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F000%2F884%2F521%2F353.gif&h=b727ef77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc45af9296ae22335a4c85c19e7371621171a08b","tid":2301492,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed112678d00f486a5827cd530079fe91acd3bbd6","tid":2301492,"uid":92859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/884/521/353.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F000%2F884%2F521%2F353.gif&h=b727ef77&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"無尊嚴的女人"},{"pid":"4fab226f62ce872ec2cabf730b4a827a0042130d","tid":2301492,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2a49c88f8a5e0a51adb9801aa6605d975c3751","tid":2301492,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"死撚埋一邊啦  CCTVB 紅媒01 打手 <br />\n<br />\non99"}]}